  <main class="clue">
    <h2><span class="glitch" data-text="Smudged Lipstick">Smudged Lipstick</span></h2>
    <img class="item-shot" src="" alt="Smudged lipstick" onerror="this.style.display='none'"/>
    <div class="body">
      <p>Red, the shade she never wore to work. The cap isn’t the one it came with—this one’s from a different brand. Someone borrowed it, or swapped it, or put it back wrong in a hurry.</p>
      <p>Along the rim, a faint gray smudge. It looks like ash. She doesn’t smoke.</p>
      <p>In the case’s tiny mirror: a thumbprint dragged across the glass, angling left. Smudged at 1:17, maybe… if the clock reflection is right.</p>
    </div>
  </main>

